          <td width="82%" valign="top">
          <section>
        
     <h1 align="center"  id="top"><b>ADMINISTRATION DIVISION</b></h1>
     <blockquote>
       <p> This Division is under the overall control of Deputy Chief Administrative Officer (Admin)/Dy CAO (A). There are 12 sections in this Division dealing with pay and allowances, leave, service records etc. of civilian employees posted in Army HQ &amp; various ISOs except those under admin control of CAO/A-2. The details of sections and charter of duties are as under :-</p>
     </blockquote>

<p>(a)<b> C AO/A-1(A)</b> Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted and Non-gazetted employees of Dte of Standardization, DGAFMS, DGAQA, Dte Gen of Resettlement, Naval Psychological Research Unit (Cochin). </p>

<p>(b) <b>CAO/A-1(B)</b> Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted and Non-gazetted employees of DIPR and DRDO (Technical and Non-Technical). </p>

<p>(c )<b> C AO/A-3(A)</b> Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted and Non-gazetted employees of DGQA (Vehicle), DGQA (Stores), DGQA (Warship Projects), DGQA (Electronics), Defence Exhibition Organization, DGQA (Engineering Equipment), KSB, Defence Library, History Division and Central Monitoring Organisation Dte.</p>

<p>(d) <b>CAO/A-3(B)</b> Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted and Non-gazetted employees of DGQA (Adm), DGQA (Armaments), DGQA (Naval), Dte of Planning &amp; Coordination. </p>

<p>(e) <b>CAO/A-4(A)</b> Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted and Non-Gazetted employees of QMG Branch. </p>

<p>(f) <b>CAO/A-4(B)</b> Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted and Non-Gazetted employees of MGO Branch.</p>

<p>(g) <b>CAO/A-5(A)</b></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>(i) Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted officers of AG’s Branch, DG/ADG system, Ordnance Factory Cell, Service Sports Control Board; and,</p>
  <p>(ii) Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Non- Gazetted employees of AG/Coord and Registry, AG/Ceremonial and Welfare Dte., AG/Personnel Services Dte, AG/MP Dte., AG/JAG’s Branch, AG/Provost Marshal’s Dte, AG/Medical and AG/Dental.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>(h) <b>CAO/A-5(B)</b></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>(i) Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Non-Gazetted employees of AG/Recruiting Dte, AG/ Discipline and Vigilance Dte, GS/ADG Systems, MGO (Central Provisioning Cell) Store Keepers Deptt., Ordnance Factory Cell, Dte General of Ordnance Factories, OFC/OFB Staff, Services Sports Control Board; and,</p>
  <p>(ii) Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted &amp; Non Gazetted employees GS/Inf, GS/DG Mech Forces (Pers), Armed Forces Film Photo Division &amp; Ministry of Defence Distribution Section.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>(i ) <b>CAO/A-6(A) </b>Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted &amp; Non Gazetted employees of E-in-C’s Branch, MES, National War Memorial Museum, College of Military Engineering, Project Management Office (Defence), Image Processing and Analysis Centre.</p>

<p>(j) <b>CAO/A-6(B)</b></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>(i) Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted &amp; Non- Gazetted employees of HQ IDS, GS/SI Dte, GS/MI Dte; and,</p>
  <p>(ii) Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted and Non -Gazetted employees including Non-AFHQ Officers &amp; employees of Directorate of Public Relation.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>(k) <b>CAO/A-7(A) </b>Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Gazetted officers of GS Branch {(except ADG Systems, Inf, GS/SI, GS/MI and DGMS (Pers)}, MS Branch, School of Foreign Languages, QMG (Adm &amp; Coord) and Non-gazetted employees of MS Branch, SFL.</p>

<p>(l) <b>CAO/A-7(B) </b>Processing of all Administrative work, pay &amp; allowances of all Non-gazetted employees of General Staff Branch, {(except ADG System, Inf, DGMS(Pers), GS/MI and GS/SI} and QMG (Adm &amp; Coord).</p>
          </section>
          
            
